##A QUARANTINED PERSON'S SELF-STATEMENT: Thirty years from Hubei "fled" back to Hangzhou, I shed countless tears

WECHAT goodlife225

Functional Introduction, the relentless years, there is love.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
Hubei is my hometown, Hangzhou is my home

Dictation archimedes

From Hubei back to Hangzhou, my family of three began 14 days of isolation.
I thought I might be discriminated against, as I was
The community said, "We will guarantee your privacy and thank you for your cooperation. "
Property said: "You were wronged, thank you for your understanding. "
This city of warmth and commitment is the home I love.

01
Change the return journey again and again, finally escape the "closed city"
18 January

The three of US got up at five o'clock that morning. I haven't been back to my hometown in Hubei Province for two years. I had no idea that this journey would be so difficult.
Before setting out, my husband reminded us that the Chunyun railway station was crowded and the air was bad, so the adults and children put on masks and set out.
My family returned to Hangzhou from Anlu in the 30s

The Rickety Green train took us to Wuchang Railway Station, where our family was still heavily armed and masked. Fewer people travel on the green train these days, few get off in Wuchang Railway Station, and few wear face masks. We got out of the car and headed to the underground parking lot where our family was waiting for us.
My hometown in Anlu, Hubei Province, drove more than two hours, finally arrived at the home of longing, relatives have prepared delicious food in US, really happy.
No one would have thought that one day later, the weather in Hubei would change.
January 20th
In the evening, Academician Zhong Nanshan mentioned the Wuhan epidemic in the news. That night, the children's kindergarten sent a message to calculate the travel situation of the children. We and our brother and sister-in-law became alert.
I ordered more than 100 masks and disinfectant for my family and booked a return ticket from Wuhan instead of Yichang. I said to my father, do not come back with Wuhan relatives to eat, also do not move around.
Soon the cities of Wuhan, Huanggang and Red Cliff began to close, and the situation was even worse than we thought.
24 January

ÅŒmisoka. Early in the morning I placed an order online, to the home of the store of rice, oil, vegetables, water and other necessities of life. At breakfast, we began to worry about how to get back to work in Hangzhou in case the place was closed. You never know how long you're GONNA get. You can't have two people out of work.
Zhejiang's relatives also a phone call to a phone call to urge, can come back as soon as possible.
Relatives in the family have been sending news, first home in Guangzhou, said the third uncle bought a ticket to go back, and soon set off, then in Shenzhen to work cousin said to prepare to drive back to Shenzhen immediately. I quickly looked at the train ticket information, actually there are two back to Hangzhou train, the afternoon through our city, and there are tickets.
Dad said, then quickly bought to go, do not go, I am afraid not to go. You don't have to worry about us. We're fine. We're not going anywhere.
Return train ticket

I got a hard sleeper on the 4:00 pm train.
We had a hurried lunch and began to pack. I held my mother cried a lot, I said, mom, I really want to be at home with you ah, we did not eat dinner. Mother said, silly child, you and xx have a home and work in Hangzhou, we can't support you all your life, always have to go back.
Her husband reported to the unit back to Hangzhou News, the daughter also called the kindergarten teacher, said she would go home to Hangzhou, home will be a good isolation. The teacher told the child must wear a mask on the way, the daughter also promised to sleep wearing.
My brother drove us to the train station, and we put on double masks and carried our suitcases into the station. Family, don't come in and see us off. No.
The family returned wearing masks

Back home in the train station, this time no one took the temperature. It was a small station, and there were not many people coming and going. Everyone was wearing masks and very quiet.
The three of US stood in the corner, as far away from people as possible, further away. Suddenly, I heard someone calling my name. I turned my head and saw it was my father. He was wearing a mask and waving at me through the waiting-room window.
I couldn't help but weep again, and waved my hand to my father to hurry home.
The train from Chengdu to Shanghai had many stops in Hubei Province, but when we boarded it, only our city and another city were open and accessible. That night, our city was closed.
Report to the community on the way

After getting in the car, I reported back home to the community in Hangzhou and told them to prepare to quarantine themselves when they arrived in Hangzhou. The community expressed understanding and told us that they would arrange for our doctor to take our temperature at home. They hoped that we would cooperate actively.
The community also said they would guarantee our privacy.
The last few days have been explaining coronavirus to the child, she has certain knowledge, so all the way has been extremely well-behaved. The soft sleeper was so hot that the three of us shut the door and could hardly go out except to the toilet.
My daughter wears a mask even when she sleeps

Daughter really even sleep wearing a mask, small face red, looked really painful.
The conductor came and said it was time to make dinner reservations. I don't have an appetite, but it's New Year's Eve, and I need a hot meal, and so do the kids.
I had a memorable New Year's Eve dinner on the train

The whole family ordered a drumstick set meal and the three of US finished the unforgettable New Year's Eve dinner.

02
The community property is serious to wait for, the isolation life feels warm
25 January

The train arrives in Hangzhou in the morning.
We spent more than 100 yuan to take a taxi back to our suburban home, and saved our tickets.
After arriving home, the whole family bathes, the article disinfects.
While I was washing my hair, the community doctor, the community worker, the property came.
The whole family quickly put on their masks and opened the door for our first guests of the New Year.
The community doctor took our temperature, registered information, and issued a vaccination notice. I said there were only a few masks left at home, and the community doctor gave me a pack of disposable masks, which they said they didn't have much left.
The community and the property told us not to go out for 14 days. If you have any problems, just tell them.
After the community left, we cooked noodles for a simple meal, I used the grocery APP to buy some essentials, and started a family meeting.
The moderator, my daughter, said the theme was: Enhancing Security Awareness.
Record body temperature every day

All three men defined their roles for the next 14 days. For example, the daughter's job was to stay in the house, the mother's job was to fix the doll's hair, the mother's job was to prepare every meal, the father's job was to monitor his temperature, do the dishes and sweep the floor
26 January
The young man who bought the food APP still delivered food to the door at this time. As soon as he heard them knocking on the door, my husband shouted, "put it in the doorway! "
It's OK to eat, but it's not OK to take out the garbage. You can't leave it at home to stink. I wechat and property help, ask them to help put out the garbage at the door.

Dialogue with property

The property manager said yes, he also said: "wronged you, thank you for your understanding and cooperation. "
The sweet words made me cry again.
27 January

Soon, the entrance and exit of the community began to be strictly controlled. The property will be closed to two entrances for one, the owners need to enter and exit body temperature, express prohibited entry.
The groceries are at the gate

We couldn't get our groceries home, and when we told them, they would drop them off on our doorstep every day.
Recently the property is really very hard, the workload is very big, let them help to fetch things is really a bit embarrassed. But recently it is very difficult to buy food on the Internet, want to buy always can not complete, sometimes to buy something can only be next in the morning, next in the evening, the property is also not too troublesome, help us pick up food twice a day.
Every morning, my husband would take our temperature one by one and write it down in a notebook. And when he gets a call from the police, from the community, from the CDC, he's GonNa take us seriously. The child's kindergarten also sent a message several times, we fill in the relevant information, and report the situation of a family.
We put the garbage to the door about a meter away, and then with the property wechat, after a while he will tell us that has been cleaned up.
So is grocery shopping. Dish arrived, tell a voice with the property, they quietly put to the door a meter away, and after a while Wechat told us, has been delivered.
Vegetables from the shopping APP
We couldn't hear a thing when they came to pick up the garbage and deliver the food.
Hangzhou is the Home I love!
28 January
Although we do not go out of the door, but through the network can also receive all kinds of information.
The Hangzhou municipal government holds a daily press conference to announce the epidemic and measures. Although the number of infected people is still on the rise, people are still quite relieved.
It is particularly touching that in many places to Wuhan people, Hubei People say "No" , refused to enter, Hangzhou atmosphere to accept the closure of the city and not home to many Wuhan tourists. Their flights were re-booked to Hangzhou, which accepted them, and made no secret of the fact that it was the first to inform citizens, arranged for Wuhan travelers to be admitted to the Party School, and even arranged for a cute robot to deliver food to avoid cross-infection.
When I saw the news, I was really grateful for the word "compatriot. ".
In Our community, the Community Party Committee issues an epidemic every day, including how many people are quarantined at home, how many are quarantined in hotels.
The community also told everyone that although there is no home-separated security guards directly at the door, but the monitoring room can be seen, also want everyone to monitor each other.
It's kind of boring to stay home, especially with a 5-year-old. The kindergarten teacher told me that if the child is bored, you can call her. She is very happy.
The family did gymnastics

In order to ensure the amount of exercise children, we decided to dance at home every day, morning and evening once, morning daughter lead exercise, evening husband lead exercise.
We didn't want to make a scene downstairs, so we talked to the neighbors downstairs. She said, "jump, JUMP! "
29 January
My daughter has a craving for dumplings. But for days I did not buy her favorite frozen dumplings, flour is only half a catty. I decided to give her dumplings, a little to do a few, also counts as parent-child activities to pass the time.
Making dumplings at home

Too much water, the dumplings failed, seared the big cake.
When the neighbors found out, they immediately sent me a big bag of hand-made frozen dumplings. He knocked on my door, and I let him leave it there, and I couldn't thank him enough.
The daughter ate a bowl full of dumplings.
Night with Hubei's mother video, I worry about her, she said home all right, adequate supplies, but also can play Mahjong, my father does not go out to run, run on the treadmill. She's worried about me.
I mean, I'm doing great, I'm getting VIP treatment, I'm getting help with the garbage.
"Mom, don't worry, we're fine in Hangzhou. When this time is over, we'll go back to Hubei and give you a good year. "
